{"tid":1144107,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩學生闖丹佛市中學開槍 至少1學生死亡7傷","createTime":"2019-05-08T01:57:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T02:08:40.000Z","uid":3090,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"51c195fd044bf874a52c0792ca4743af4ce0e58c","tid":1144107,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T01:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yULCF8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyULCF8L.png&h=7a0333b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67anSfq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F67anSfq.png&h=adc89181&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n槍擊發生在丹佛一間學校。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n【新增內容】<br />\n<br />\n美國科羅拉多州丹佛市郊一間學校周二發生槍擊，兩名學生持槍闖入校園開槍，至少一名18歲學生死亡，7人受傷，兩名學生之後被捕。<br />\n<br />\n事發於海蘭牧場（Highlands Ranch）一間特許學校。警方接報後，校園附近警察派出所的警員出動，到場時仍聽到槍聲。學生被疏散到附近康樂中心，由家長接走。有人目擊一人由警員揹着離開，另一人被擔架抬走。<br />\n<br />\n事發後道格拉斯縣（Douglas County）所有學校封鎖。道格拉斯懸警方指現場情況「不穩定」，呼籲公眾避免到該區。<br />\n<br />\n事發學校開辦幼稚園班至12年級班，有1,850名學生，距同州另一城市科倫拜恩（Columbine）12公里。科倫拜恩1999年4月20日發生校園槍擊，兩名學生槍殺12名學生和1名教師，24人受傷，兩人當場自殺身亡。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社／Russia Today／英國《每日郵報》／《每日鏡報》"},{"pid":"021a057022818612b2ea943bba7212fe9f3ba0d4","tid":1144107,"uid":43428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T01:58:37.000Z","msg":"又黎"},{"pid":"fd09dc8ef513d83d6406879fa04ea02987c1651d","tid":1144107,"uid":40470,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T01:59:03.000Z","msg":"好彩連登毒撚只得鍵盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3fcdd1dfcdeb745beec606a74dc3490588e270a","tid":1144107,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T01:59:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"584c60256bd0748bc0f5170fc10b757574ce5f20","tid":1144107,"uid":62350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T01:59:13.000Z","msg":"Gta咩"},{"pid":"76a56494c17d98937d08cd6c22ba20e7c31958d8","tid":1144107,"uid":